poems_df[text_column].str.contains(regex_pattern, regex=True, na=False)]\n","\n","    #Select a response\n","    if not matching_poems.empty:\n","        # we found at least one match. Lets pick one randomly.\n","        random_poem_row = matching_poems.sample(1).iloc[0]\n","        \n","        misra1 = random_poem_row['misra1']\n","        misra2 = random_poem_row['misra2']\n","        poet_name = random_poem_row['poet']\n","        \n","        return f\"{misra1}\\n{misra2}\\n\\n- {poet_name}\"\n","    \n","    else:\n","        # If the DataFrame of matches is empty, we couldn't find a reply.\n","        return f\"ุดุนุฑ ฺฉู ุจุง ุงู ุญุฑู ุดุฑูุน ุดู ูพุฏุง ูฺฉุฑุฏู \"\n"]},{"cell_type":"code","execution_count":6,"id":"a901fb3c","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.execute_input":"2025-11-14T15:38:37.787511Z","iopub.status.busy":"2025-11-14T15:38:37.787007Z","iopub.status.idle":"2025-11-14T15:38:37.795489Z","shell.execute_reply":"2025-11-14T15:38:37.794256Z"},"papermill":{"duration":0.014309,"end_time":"2025-11-14T15:38:37.797254","exception":false,"start_time":"2025-11-14T15:38:37.782945","status":"completed"},"tags":[]},"outputs":[],"source":["CONVERSATION_PATTERNS = {\n","    # hello!\n","    r\"\\b(ุณูุงู|ุฏุฑูุฏ)\": [\n","        \"ุณูุงู ุจุฑ ุดูุง! ุจุฑุง ูุดุงุนุฑู ุขูุงุฏูโุงุฏุ\",\n","        \"ุฏุฑูุฏ! ฺู ุฎูุจ ฺฉู ุงูุฌุงุฏ. ุงูุฑ ุฏุงุดุชุฏุ\",\n","        \"ุณูุงู! ุฎูุด ุขูุฏุฏ.\"\n","    ],\n","    r\"\\b(ฺุทูุฑ|ุฎูุจ|ฺู ุฎุจุฑ)\": [\n","        \"ููููู ุงุฒ ุดูุง. ูู ฺฉ ุจุฑูุงูู ูุณุชู ู ููุดู ุฏุฑ ุจูุชุฑู ุญุงู ููฺฉูู!\",\n","        \"ุนุงูโุงู ู ุขูุงุฏู ุจุฑุง ฺฉ ูุดุงุนุฑู ุฌุงูุงูู!\",\n","        \"ููู ฺุฒ ูุฑุชุจ ุงุณุช. ุดูุง ฺุทูุฑุฏุ\"\n","    ],\n","    \n","    # abalities \n","    r\"\\b(ฺฉ ูุณุช|ุงุณูุช ฺู|ูุนุฑู ฺฉู)\": [\n","        \"ูู ฺฉ ุฑุจุงุช ูุดุงุนุฑู ูุณุชู ฺฉู ุจุง ฺฏูุฌูู ุงุดุนุงุฑ ูููุงูุง